  "description": {
    "zh": "嘿，看来你现在有不错的背包了，但看起来你在负重方面有些棘手，对吧？带的东西越多，重量显然也就越大，所以好好练吧！如果你在藏身处建了一个健身区，我强烈建议你花些时间在那里训练。记住，每次从战局中带出更多物资可以为你节省很多时间。",
    "en": "Hey, cool backpacks you get there now, but it sounds like you are kinda struggling with the weight a bit, ehh? More stuff you are carrying means more weight obviously, so get some training done! If you built a place to workout in your hideout I really recommend you to spend some time there. Remember that getting more loot out of your tours at once will save you some time."
